    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Specialty paint that combines iron dust with a primer. Typically this base layer is covered with a finish paint coat in color. Magnetic paint allows for objects (usually paper) to be adhered to a surface using magnets.</Note_Text>
